### Welcome to techguy948's projects page.
Here, you can view my current projects and download them.
I am currently working on a Ultrahardcore plugin (see /r/ultrahardcore subreddit) that will allow people to use /team create IGN1,IGN2(so on) instead of bothering Admins with /helpop.

### Authors and Contributors
All credit given to @techguy948. 
This is a custom plugin for epiccheese2 and extremekiwi2012's UHC server.
